      <title>特朗普和拜登的 TikTok 盟友竞相推迟对应用的禁令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/tiktok-allies-close-to-trump-and-biden-race-to-delay-ban-on-app</link>
      <description><![CDATA[距离 TikTok 禁令颁布仅剩几天，美国两党政客都在想方设法让美国人能够继续使用这款中国拥有的视频分享应用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/tiktok-allies-close-to-trump-and-biden-race-to-delay-ban-on-app</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 06:07:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲复兴开发银行称今年可能向乌克兰投资 15 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/ebrd-says-it-may-invest-1-5-billion-in-ukraine-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于俄罗斯的持续入侵继续对乌克兰造成破坏，欧洲复兴开发银行预计未来一年对乌克兰的投资将达到 15 亿欧元（15.4 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/ebrd-says-it-may-invest-1-5-billion-in-ukraine-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国要求卢旺达停止干扰饱受战争蹂躏的刚果东部地区的 GPS 信号</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/us-demands-rwanda-stop-jamming-gps-signal-in-war-torn-east-congo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务院要求卢旺达停止在刚果民主共和国东部使用 GPS 干扰设备，该地区数百万因冲突而流离失所的人民急需援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/us-demands-rwanda-stop-jamming-gps-signal-in-war-torn-east-congo</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 05:57:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯称其破坏了乌克兰天然气储存设施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/russia-says-it-damaged-facilities-at-gas-storage-site-in-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯声称，在周三针对乌克兰能源部门的一系列袭击中，乌克兰利沃夫地区最大的天然气储存设施之一的地面基础设施遭到破坏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/russia-says-it-damaged-facilities-at-gas-storage-site-in-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 05:49:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非警方从废弃金矿中打捞出 78 具尸体</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/south-african-police-retrieve-78-bodies-from-abandoned-gold-mine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非救援人员从一座废弃的金矿中找到了 78 具尸体，数百名非法采金者在该矿与当局进行了长达数月的对峙。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/south-african-police-retrieve-78-bodies-from-abandoned-gold-mine</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 05:18:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国考虑购买更多美国能源以安抚特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/south-korea-considers-buying-more-us-energy-to-appease-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国正考虑从美国购买更多石油和天然气，以实现其能源来源多元化，并可能抵御当选总统唐纳德·特朗普提出的关税威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/south-korea-considers-buying-more-us-energy-to-appease-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 05:10:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登贸易主管警告特朗普不要依赖关税来获取收入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/trump-warned-against-relying-on-tariffs-for-cash-by-biden-trade-chief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登即将离任的贸易主管称，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普利用关税收入取代所得税的想法“非常非常危险”，并表示此举将损害低收入工人的利益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/trump-warned-against-relying-on-tariffs-for-cash-by-biden-trade-chief</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 05:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝森特财政部任命听证会值得关注的事项</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/what-to-watch-for-at-bessent-s-treasury-confirmation-hearing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部长的任命听证会通常会为提名人上任后的优先事项和原则定下关键标志，周四的参议院财政委员会听证会成为焦点，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普将挑选斯科特·贝森特 (Scott Bessent) 出任财政部长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/what-to-watch-for-at-bessent-s-treasury-confirmation-hearing</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 05:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港考虑第二年提高高收入者税负</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/hong-kong-weighs-raising-taxes-on-top-earners-for-second-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，香港政府正在研究连续第二年对香港高收入者提高税收，以弥补预算赤字。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/hong-kong-weighs-raising-taxes-on-top-earners-for-second-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 01:15:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列与哈马斯达成停火协议暂停加沙战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/israel-hamas-agree-gaza-ceasefire-deal-in-wind-down-of-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列和哈马斯同意释放数十名人质并暂停加沙战争。过去 15 个月来，加沙战争已造成数万人死亡，并引发了整个中东地区的混乱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/israel-hamas-agree-gaza-ceasefire-deal-in-wind-down-of-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 17:00:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
